A bodybuilder – Lee Little – said that steroids have made him infertile. He said that he would have liked to have kids but now can’t. He has taken steroids for 25 years and started because he wanted to build his confidence. [eap_ad_1]He admitted that he was bullied when he was younger and started training at 13 to feel better about himself. He also said that he has had depression. (BBC)[eap_ad_4]